msgid ""
"Inside the OTOBO standard system, the option "
"Ticket::Frontend::NeedAccountedTime overrides the option "
"Action::NoteMandatory. Therefore, it is not possible to configure "
"dialogues without mandatory entry of articles and TimeUnits. This package"
" changes the behaviour, TimeUnits are only mandatory if an article exists"
" for it."
